Carrefour Says Annual Savings From Brazil Merger Could Reach $1.1 Billion

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-07-04T05:36:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/carrefour-says-annual-savings-from-brazil-merger-could-reach-1-1-billion.html
Carrefour SA (CA)  said its board approved
a plan to merge its Brazilian assets with Cia. Brasileira de
Distribuicao Grupo Pao de Acucar and estimated annual savings
from the operation at between 600 million euros and 800 million
euros a year.  The news came in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  